Package: skellambrms
Title: Symmetric Skellam Distribution as a brms Custom Family
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Adam N. H.", "Smith", , "anhsmith@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides the symmetric Skellam distribution — the distribution
    of the difference of two independent Poisson random variables with equal
    rates — as a custom family for brms. Intended for modelling set-level
    differences between paired count sources.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports:
    brms,
    skellam
Suggests:
    rstan,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/anhsmith/skellambrms
